'You can say more. I will not judge the shape of the story.',
'That matters because it is affecting you. What part feels most important to say first?',
'I may not fully understand yet. Can you tell me what happened and what you need from me right now?',
'You do not have to solve this in one message. We can take it one piece at a time.',
'Thank you for trusting this space with that. What feels heaviest about it?'
